{"id": "art-207", "label": "Art. 207", "title": "Art. 207", "slug": "art-207", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 207 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Capitalul social poate fi redus prin:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)<span\nclass=SpellE>mic&#351;orarea</span> num&#259;rului de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> sociale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)reducerea\nvalorii nominale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> sau a <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)dobândirea\npropriilor <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, urmat&#259; de anularea lor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Capitalul social mai poate fi redus, atunci când reducerea nu este\nmotivat&#259; de pierderi, prin:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)scutirea\ntotal&#259; sau <span class=SpellE>par&#355;ial&#259;</span> a <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> de v&#259;rs&#259;mintele datorate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)restituirea\nc&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span> a unei cote-<span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> din aporturi, <span class=SpellE>propor&#355;ional&#259;</span>\ncu reducerea capitalului social <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncalculat&#259; egal pentru fiecare <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iune</span> sau\nparte social&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)alte\nprocedee prev&#259;zute de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>.</span></p>"}